'''Domain Hool''' was a [[Domain]] among the [[Shaper caste]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. Domain Hool was placed in charge of [[Terraforming/Legends|Vongforming]] [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] into [[Coruscant/Legends#Yuuzhan'tar|Yuuzhan'tar]], until [[Supreme Overlord]] [[Shimrra Jamaane|Shimrra]] executed [[Ch'Gang Hool]] for incompetence, blaming him for the "plagues" that had been affecting the worldshaping. In reality these were conscious acts of sabotage committed by the [[World Brain]] at [[Darth Caedus|Jacen Solo's]] behest.

